&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Nebius:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nebius is leading a new era in cloud infrastructure for the global AI economy. We are building a full-stack AI cloud platform that supports developers and enterprises from data and model training through to production deployment, without the cost and complexity of building large in-house AI/ML infrastructure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Built by engineers, for engineers. From large-scale GPU orchestration to inference optimization, we own the hard problems across compute, storage, networking and applied AI.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Listed on Nasdaq (NBIS) and headquartered in Amsterdam, we have a global footprint with R&amp;amp;D hubs across Europe, the UK, North America and Israel. Our team of 1,500+ includes hundreds of engineers with deep expertise across hardware, software and AI R&amp;amp;D.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;The role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Accounts Receivable Analyst will be responsible for driving data-based insights, automation, and analytical excellence within the Accounts Receivable (AR) domain.&amp;nbsp; This role plays a key part in strengthening financial accuracy, improving receivables processes, and supporting strategic decision-making across Finance.&amp;nbsp; The AR Analyst will independently manage end-to-end analytical processes — from data modeling and reconciliation automation to performance reporting — while partnering with cross-functional stakeholders to ensure data integrity and operational efficiency.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;Strong&quot;&gt;Your responsibilities will include:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Analytical &amp;amp; Strategic Finance Support&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze AR and revenue data to identify patterns, forecast trends, and highlight process improvement opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop dashboards and analytical models to monitor receivables health, DSO performance, and collection efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide actionable insights and recommendations to support strategic decision-making in Finance and Business Operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Process Optimization &amp;amp; Automation&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, implement, and maintain automated AR data workflows and reconciliation tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Accounting and Engineering teams to streamline data pipelines between ERP (NetSuite) and reporting systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously improve data accuracy, reconciliation speed, and operational efficiency through automation and analytical solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reporting &amp;amp; Data Visualization&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain BI dashboards and reports (e.g., Power BI, Tableau, or Looker) providing visibility into receivables, revenue timing, and intercompany transactions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate complex financial data into clear and concise management insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support monthly and quarterly closing with data validation, variance analysis, and reconciliation analytics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional Collaboration&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Accounting, Treasury, and Business Operations teams to ensure consistent AR data definitions and accuracy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Data and Engineering teams to enhance system integrations and data quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Co

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Nebius:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nebius is leading a new era in cloud infrastructure for the global AI economy. We are building a full-stack AI cloud platform that supports developers and enterprises from data and model training through to production deployment, without the cost and complexity of building large in-house AI/ML infrastructure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Built by engineers, for engineers. From large-scale GPU orchestration to inference optimization, we own the hard problems across compute, storage, networking and applied AI.&lt;/p&gt;
