&lt;li&gt;Ensure the availability and reliability of mechanical, electrical, plumbing, and life safety systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain compliance with Service Level Agreements (SLAs) and uptime objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee 24/7 operational support, including incident response and escalation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure all Standard Operating Procedures (SOPs), Emergency Operating Procedures (EOPs), and Method of Procedures (MOPs) are current and followed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Leadership &amp;amp; Team Management&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead, mentor, and develop Critical Facilities Engineers and Technicians.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage shift schedules, staffing, training, and performance evaluations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foster a culture of safety, accountability, teamwork, and continuous improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate contractor and vendor activities to ensure quality and compliance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Maintenance &amp;amp; Asset Management&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and oversee preventive, predictive, and corrective maintenance programs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage maintenance planning through the Computerized Maintenance Management System (CMMS).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor equipment lifecycle performance and develop replacement strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure maintenance activities minimize operational risk and downtime.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Infrastructure Management&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;Oversee the operation and maintenance of:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Electrical distribution systems (MV/LV)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;UPS systems and battery plants&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Standby diesel generators&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Automatic Transfer Switches (ATS)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Chillers and chilled water systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CRAH and CRAC units&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Air Handling Units (AHUs)&lt;/li&gt;
